# Git Push Target (Backend Repo)

- Repository: `jobs-service-backend`
- Default working branch: `main`
- Default push target: `origin main`

## Commit/Push Guidance

- Push backend commits to `main` in this repository, unless the user explicitly requests a different branch.
- Keep backend commits scoped to backend files only.
